    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Cell
    A Cell is a part of a grid-based maze.
    ErrorView
    ErrorView is a utility class for displaying styled error popup dialogs in a JavaFX application.
    GenerationController
    GenerationController handles maze generation and loading from files It manages user input, initializes the maze and UI components
    GenerationView
    GenerationView is the JavaFX user interface class for maze generation configuration.
    Main
    Entry point for the Maze Generation and Resolution JavaFX application.
    Maze
    The Maze class represents a rectangular grid of cells used in maze generation and solving.
    MazeController
    MazeController manages the generation and solving of mazes.
    MazeController.GenerationListener
    Listener interface for maze generation completion.
    MazeController.SolvingListener
    Listener interface for maze solving completion.
    MazeGenerator
    Class responsible for generating mazes using specific algorithms.
    MazeGeneratorDFS
    MazeGeneratorDFS is a maze generation algorithm that uses Depth-First Search (DFS) to generate a random maze.
    MazeGeneratorKruskal
    Maze generator using Kruskal's algorithm using Union-Find data structure It starts with each cell as an individual set and removes walls between randoms adjacent cells that belong to different sets, forming a minimum spanning tree
    MazeGeneratorPrim
    Implements Prim's algorithm Starts from a random cell, connects it to a visted neighbor and adds its unvisited neigbors to the frontier
    MazeView
    MazeView is a JavaFX component that visually represents a maze on a canvas.
    ModificationController
    ModificationController handles user interactions for modifying the maze like changing walls, the start and the end It manages a copy of the original maze, applies changes via user clicks, and saves the modifications back into the original maze
    ModificationController.Mode
    Enum representing the modification modes.
    ModificationView
    ModificationView provides a user interface for manually modifying a maze.
    ResolverController
     
    ResolverView
    ResolverView is the JavaFX interface for solving mazes.
